{"tid":2242706,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"討論甚麼是Cult片??( 翻生爭霸戰 , 逃出立法院 )","createTime":"2020-10-14T07:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T09:40:00.000Z","uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3e1e794fa91b6d33b1c7920effa1316a9bb4509a","tid":2242706,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T07:49:26.000Z","msg":"討論甚麼是Cult片??( 翻生爭霸戰 , 逃出立法院 )<br />\n<br />\n冥通銀行特約：翻生爭霸戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yWxEvqd324Q&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyWxEvqd324Q%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2kv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=1d12d88f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yWxEvqd324Q&amp;feature=emb_logo</a><br />\n<br />\n逃出立法院<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=09-x9_G9WzA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D09-x9_G9WzA&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2kv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=f1a2fe87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=09-x9_G9WzA</a><br />\n<br />\n其實點樣定義呢套係Cult片??<br />\n以&quot;翻生爭霸戰&quot;同&quot;逃出立法院&quot;比較, <br />\n我會講&quot;逃出立法院&quot;係cult片.<br />\n&quot;翻生爭霸戰&quot;某程度上不屬於Cult片.<br />\n<br />\n我覺得Cult片定義=&gt;<br />\n1) Cult片好多時題材古怪, 但題材古怪唔一定係cult片.<br />\n&quot;翻生爭霸戰&quot;同&quot;逃出立法院&quot;,呢兩套都係題材古怪.<br />\n2) 人物性格誇張,明顯&quot;翻生爭霸戰&quot;既人物性格,<br />\n無&quot;逃出立法院&quot;咁誇張.<br />\n3) 故事情節同過程誇張.雖然&quot;翻生爭霸戰&quot;情節係誇張,<br />\n但故事過程比較公式化.同無一種離普,有無攪錯既感覺.<br />\n相反&quot;逃出立法院&quot;故事過程誇張.同卡通化.<br />\n<br />\n以戲論戲<br />\n冥通銀行特約：翻生爭霸戰 <br />\n=&gt; 題材幾攪事, 但拍出來好傳統同正常.<br />\n樣樣都想講D.<br />\n變得無咩野突出,睇完覺得平淡.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;逃出立法院&quot;相對cult到盡,玩到盡.<br />\n有唔少笑位. 人物性格會有印象.<br />\n當然唔喜歡cult會覺得佢垃圾<br />\n<br />\n&quot;逃出立法院&quot;好過&quot;翻生爭霸戰&quot;,<br />\n因為&quot;翻生爭霸戰&quot;無明顯定位.<br />\nCult片又cult唔晒(玩野不足), 驚嚇不足, 感情線平淡.<br />\n幾頭唔到岸."},{"pid":"c9facaddbfaf24d3e05fb88ae8dd4847e3b8fa8b","tid":2242706,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:24:40.000Z","msg":"逃出立法院好垃圾"},{"pid":"cb1b1ab0cee5c4e33a9576a7b0ce570443479344","tid":2242706,"uid":34965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T10:50:10.000Z","msg":"其實cult片係要上畫／發行後引起某一堆人熱烈崇拜<br />\n所以嚴格來講一套戲未上前唔可以算cult片？<br />\n不過因為呢d戲多數都有d古怪元素，無論呈現手法定題材<br />\n漸漸cult片個字既定義都變左質，所以我覺得個界線都幾模糊<br />\n我自己會覺得精神上夠癲先算，無論佢好唔好<br />\n如果玩style但個文本好正經都唔算"},{"pid":"de3aee455e2eaa0fb46323c7e19c7afc536cb341","tid":2242706,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:40:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Bm7MtPNFMKt/?igshid=2mrfte9zavy6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBm7MtPNFMKt%2F%3Figshid%3D2mrfte9zavy6&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2kv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=750da038\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBm7MtPNFMKt%2F%3Figshid%3D2mrfte9zavy6&h=e9ed1304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/Bm7MtPNFMKt/?igshid=2mrfte9zavy6</a>"}]}